com.blukii.sdk.info

Class BlukiiClient.OnResolveServerNewsListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.blukii.sdk.info.BlukiiClient.OnResolveServerNewsListener
  • Enclosing class:
    BlukiiClient

    public abstract static class BlukiiClient.OnResolveServerNewsListener
extends java.lang.Object

    Callbacks for retrieving a translated blukii Info Manager news text.



    The callbacks are registered by calling BlukiiClient.resolveServerNews(String, OnResolveServerNewsListener).
    See Also:
    BlukiiClient.resolveServerNews(String, OnResolveServerNewsListener)

      • onError

        public void onError(BlukiiClient.ErrorCode errorCode)
        Will be called once after calling BlukiiClient.resolveServerNews(String, OnResolveServerNewsListener).

        If the element can successfully be resolved , onNewsResult(String) will be called instead.
        Parameters:
        errorCode - error code

      • onNewsResult

        public void onNewsResult(java.lang.String news)
        Will be called once after calling BlukiiClient.resolveServerNews(String, OnResolveServerNewsListener).

        If the element can not be resolved because of no data or any error, onError(com.blukii.sdk.info.BlukiiClient.ErrorCode) will be called instead.
        Parameters:
        news - translated news text
